{"tid":298265,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉曉波確診末期肝癌　已申請保外就醫","createTime":"2017-06-26T07:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T07:37:26.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"796c9ac15b25efca8a45358dc087626d4fdcf953","tid":298265,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:20:40.000Z","msg":"據了解，因煽動顛覆國家政權罪被判監11年的諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波，確診患有末期肝癌，並已申請保外就醫，現時在瀋陽中國醫科大學附屬一院救治。<br />\n<br />\n在遼寧錦州監獄服刑的劉曉波，代表律師尚寶軍確認，劉曉波是在5月底得悉確診患有肝癌。劉曉波另一位律師莫少平指，消息是劉曉波的弟弟劉曉暄透露，劉曉暄曾赴醫院探望。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉波是內地著名異見人士，1989年六四事件期間，是帶領絕食的廣場四君子之一，六四事件後多次被捕。劉曉波在2008年起草《零八憲章》，要求當局給予言論自由、人權和民主，翌年被判以煽動顛覆國家政權罪被判監11年。2010年獲頒發諾貝爾和平獎，是首位獲該獎的中華人民共和國公民。"},{"pid":"83c1a90eaac9c1b4bfb2df7e4bb35bb53d30eedc","tid":298265,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1338298-20170626.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1338298-20170626.htm&d=8rR%2BWoJwS7HT%2F4RB%2BlRf7hxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=271f422a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1338298-20170626.htm&h=31363e5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1338298-20170626.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5f9815753b3e000ed10d42e5275d71d447e41107","tid":298265,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"泛民又可以話自己成功爭取啦, <br />\n又可以話六四維園鳩坐有用啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}